title: Shingeki no Kyojin (Attack on Titan) Manga Chapter 44-47 (jpg)
description:
This is Shingeki no Kyojin - The complete English Manga from chapters 44 through to chapter 47 . This is an awesome manga, and is very hard to come by, so please enjoy it to the fullest. The quality is quite high and it is in 4 folders, of each roughly  around 45.png's per chapter. Please note this is in .jpg format and not in .cbr or a comic book reader format, so please be aware of this. 

If you would like to have it in .cbr format, and you are on a windows computer - the following steps can show you how to quickly covert it without any programs.

1. compress each folder - e.g. 1-4.RAR
2. make sure 'hide known file extensions' is UNticked.
3. change the .RAR extension to a .CBR extension, and wallah!! you have comic book reader formats.



Show: Shingeki no Kyojin
Chapters: 44-47
Folders: 4
Format: .jpg images
size: ~100mb
